caption.title: Related to Fig 1. WT NS1 but not the NS1-N207Q mutant increase the permeability of HPMEC and HBMEC monolayers.
caption.p: Transendothelial electrical resistance (TEER) assays were used to determine the effect of the NS1-N207Q mutant on NS1-induced hyperpermeability. TEER data here are the non-normalized raw data from Fig 1 displayed in Ohms (Î©). (A) HPMEC values from Fig 1E and (B) HBMEC values from Fig 1F.
